{
  "If v(t) = 3t^2 - 6t represents velocity in m/s, what is the net displacement from t = 0 to t = 4?": "如果 v(t) = 3t%2 - 6t 表示 m/s 速度,那么从 t = 0 到 t = 4 的净移位是多少?",
  "8 meters": "8米 8米",
  "32 meters": "32米",
  "16 meters": "16米 16米",
  "0 meters": "0米",
  "Net displacement = integral from 0 to 4 of (3t^2 - 6t) dt = [t^3 - 3t^2] from 0 to 4 = (64 - 48) - 0 = 16 meters.": "净置换=0至4(3吨2 - 6吨) dt = 0至4 (64 - 48) - 0 = 16米的零至4(3吨3 - 3吨2) = [吨3 - 3吨2] = (64 - 48) - 0 = 16米。",
  "A population grows at rate P'(t) = 100 + 20t people per year. Find the net change in population from t = 0 to t = 5.": "人口以P'(t) = 100 + 20t = 年增长率增长。 找出人口净变化从 t = 0 到 t = 5。",
  "500 people": "500人(500人)",
  "200 people": "200人",
  "750 people": "750人 750人",
  "1000 people": "1000人 1000人",
  "Net change = integral from 0 to 5 of (100 + 20t) dt = [100t + 10t^2] from 0 to 5 = 500 + 250 = 750 people.": "净变动=0至5(100+20t) dt=[100t+10t%2],0至5=500+250=750人之间,从0至5(100+20t) dt=[100t+10t%2]之间,从0至5=500+250=750人之间。",
  "Water flows into a tank at rate R(t) = 4t gallons per minute. How much water enters from t = 1 to t = 3?": "水流以R(t) = 每分钟4吨加仑的速度流入罐体,从t = 1到t = 3有多少水流入?",
  "8 gallons": "8加仑",
  "12 gallons": "12加仑",
  "16 gallons": "16加仑",
  "24 gallons": "24加仑",
  "Amount = integral from 1 to 3 of 4t dt = [2t^2] from 1 to 3 = 18 - 2 = 16 gallons.": "数量 = 4t dt 4t = [2t2] 2,1 = 3 = 18-2 = 16加仑中1至3的有机体。",
  "If F'(x) = 2x + 5 and F(1) = 10, what is F(4)?": "如果F'(x)=2x+5和F(1)=10,F(4)是什么?",
  "21.5": "21.5",
  "25": "25 25",
  "40": "40个 40个",
  "31.5": "31.5 31.5",
  "F(4) = F(1) + integral from 1 to 4 of (2x + 5) dx = 10 + [x^2 + 5x] from 1 to 4 = 10 + (16 + 20 - 1 - 5) = 10 + 30 - 6... Let me recompute: [x^2 + 5x] from 1 to 4 = (16+20) - (1+5) = 36 - 6 = 30. Hmm wait: at x=4: 16+20=36. At x=1: 1+5=6. So integral = 30. F(4) = 10 + 30 = 40. Actually let me recheck the answer. F(4) = 10 + integral from 1 to 4 of (2x+5) dx = 10 + [x^2+5x] evaluated from 1 to 4 = 10 + (36-6) = 10 + 30 = 40. So the answer should be 40.": "F(4) = F(1) + 从1 = 1 至 4 2 + 5 dx = 10 + [xx2 + 5x] 从 1 = 4 = 10 + (16 + 20 - 1 - 5) = 10 + + 30 - 6... 让我重新计算: [xx2 + 5x] 从 1 = 4 = (16+ 20 - 5) = 36 - 6 = 30 = 30 hmm wait: at x = 4: 16+ 20= 36。 在 x = 1 1 + + 5= 6. 所以 = 30 F(4) = 10 + 30 = 40。",
  "A car's velocity is v(t) = 60 - 10t mph. What is the total distance traveled from t = 0 to t = 8 hours?": "汽车的速度是 v(t) = 60 - 10t mph. 从t = 0到 t = 8 小时的总距离是多少?",
  "160 miles": "160英里 160英里",
  "80 miles": "80英里 80英里",
  "320 miles": "320英里",
  "200 miles": "200英里",
  "v(t) = 0 at t = 6. Total distance = integral from 0 to 6 of (60-10t) dt + integral from 6 to 8 of |60-10t| dt = [60t-5t^2] from 0 to 6 + integral from 6 to 8 of (10t-60) dt = 180 + [5t^2-60t] from 6 to 8 = 180 + (320-480-180+360) = 180 + 20 = 200 miles.": "v(t) = 0 at t = 6. 总距离 = 0 至 6 (60-10t) dt + 6-8 (60-10t dt = [60t-5t%2] 0 + 6-8 (10t-60dt = 180+ [5t-2-60t] = 180+ (320-480-180+360) = 180 + 20 = 200英里。",
  "The rate of oil leaking from a tank is R(t) = 100e^(-0.1t) gallons per hour. How much oil leaks in the first 10 hours?": "罐体漏油的速度是 R(t) = 100e(-0.1吨) 每小时100加仑。 头10小时漏油多少?",
  "100(1 - e^(-1)) gallons": "100(1 - e(-1) 加仑",
  "1000 gallons": "1000加仑",
  "1000(1 - e^(-1)) gallons": "1000(1 - e(-1) 加仑",
  "100 gallons": "100加仑",
  "Integral from 0 to 10 of 100e^(-0.1t) dt = [-1000e^(-0.1t)] from 0 to 10 = -1000e^(-1) + 1000 = 1000(1 - e^(-1)) approximately 632 gallons.": "100e(-0.1t) dt = [-1000e(-0.1t)] 0 = 10 = - 10000e(-1) + 1000 = 1000(1 - e(-1)) 约632加仑。",
  "A company's marginal revenue is R'(x) = 50 - 0.1x. What is the revenue gained from selling units 100 to 200?": "一个公司的边际收入是R'(x) = 50 - 0.1x. 销售单位100到200所得的收入是多少?",
  "$2500": "2500美元",
  "$3500": "3 500美元",
