  "Net rate = 120 - 80 = 40 mL/hr. Net change over 5 hours = 40 * 5 = 200 mL. Total = 3000 + 200 = 3200 mL.": "净汇率=120-80=40毫升/小时; 5小时净变化=40 * 5=200毫升; 总计=300+200=3200毫升。",
  "A company's profit rate is P'(t) = 1000 - 200t dollars per month. Starting with $0 profit, find the maximum accumulated profit and when it occurs.": "公司的利润率是P'(t) = 1000 - 200美元/月,从0美元利润开始,找到最大累计利润,并在达到该利润时找到。",
  "$5000 at t = 10 months": "500 000美元t = 10个月",
  "Maximum profit of $2500 at t = 5 months": "最大利润2500美元,t = 5个月",
  "$1000 at t = 1 month": "1 000美元t = 1个月",
  "$2000 at t = 4 months": "T = 4个月= 4个月",
  "P'(t) = 0 at t = 5. P(5) = integral from 0 to 5 of (1000-200t) dt = [1000t-100t^2] from 0 to 5 = 5000-2500 = $2500. After t = 5, P'(t) < 0 so profit decreases.": "P'(t) = 0 at t = 0 = 0 at = 5. P(5) = 0 至 5 (1000-200t) dt = [1000t-100t] dt = [1000t-100t+2] 0 = 5 = 5000-2500 = 2 500美元。t = 5, P'(t) = 0 = 利润下降。",
  "An athlete runs with velocity v(t) = 10 - 2|t - 3| m/s for 0 <= t <= 6. Find the total distance covered.": "以速度 v(t) = 10 - 2t - 3m/s 运行的运动员, 0 t = 6. 找出总距离。",
  "42 meters": "42米42米",
