  "For 0 <= t <= 3: v(t) = 10-2(3-t) = 4+2t. For 3 <= t <= 6: v(t) = 10-2(t-3) = 16-2t. Both are positive on [0,6]. Distance = integral from 0 to 3 of (4+2t) dt + integral from 3 to 6 of (16-2t) dt = [4t+t^2] from 0 to 3 + [16t-t^2] from 3 to 6 = (12+9) + (96-36-48+9) = 21 + 21 = 42 meters.": "0 t 3: v(t) = 102(3-t) = 4+2t。 3  t = 6: v(t) = 102(t) = 16-2t = 16-2t = 0至 3: v(t) = 10.2-3-t = 4+2t。 3  t = 6: v(t) = 102(t) = 10(t) = 16-2t = 16-22; 3 = 6: (12+9) + (96-36-48+9) = 21+ 21= 42米。",
  "A city's electricity consumption rate is E(t) = 500 + 200 sin(pi*t/12) MW, where t is hours after midnight. Find the total electricity consumed in a 24-hour day.": "城市的电力消耗率为E(t) = 500+ 200 sin(pi*t/12) MW, 午夜后几小时为t。",
  "16,800 MWh": "16 800兆瓦h",
