  "14,400 MWh": "14 400兆瓦小时",
  "Integral from 0 to 24 of (500+200sin(pi*t/12)) dt = [500t - 200(12/pi)cos(pi*t/12)] from 0 to 24 = 12000 - (2400/pi)(cos(2pi)-cos(0)) = 12000 - (2400/pi)(1-1) = 12000 MWh. The sine term integrates to zero over a full period.": "(500+200sin (pi*t/12)) dt = [500t - 200(12/pi)cos (pi*/12)] = 0 24 = 12000 - 2400/pi (cos (2pi)-cos (0)) = 12000 - 2400/pi (1-1) = 12000 MWh。",
  "Snow accumulates on a driveway at rate S(t) = 2 + cos(t) inches per hour and is shoveled at a constant rate of 1.5 inches per hour (for t > 2). Find the net snow depth at t = 4 if S starts at t = 0 and shoveling starts at t = 2.": "雪以S(t) = 2 + cos(t) 英寸/小时的速度积聚在车道上,以每小时1.5英寸的恒定速率铲雪(t > 2) 。 如果S = 0 = 0 开始铲雪,则在 t = 2 开始铲雪,则在 t = 4 处寻找净雪深。",
  "integral from 0 to 2 of (2+cos(t)) dt + integral from 2 to 4 of (2+cos(t)-1.5) dt = (4+sin(2)) + (1+sin(4)-sin(2)) = 5+sin(4)": "从0到2 (2+cos(t) dt + 2+ 4 (2+cos(t)-1.5) dt = (4+sin(2)) + 1+sin(4)-sin(2)) = 5+sin(4) = 5+sin(4)) = 2+4 dt = 2+4 (2+cos(t)-1.5) dt = (4+sin(2)) + 1+sin(4)-sin(2)) = 5+sin(4)",
  "8 inches when the interaction between rate and Accumulation factors is taken into full account": "8英寸,其中充分考虑到汇率和累计系数之间的相互作用",
  "6 inches, particularly when rate considerations are weighed against competing pressures": "6英寸,特别是当将比率考虑与相互竞争的压力相权衡时",
  "4 inches, particularly when rate considerations are weighed against competing pressures": "4英寸,特别是当将比率考虑与相互竞争的压力相权衡时",
  "From 0 to 2: net rate = 2+cos(t). Accumulation = [2t+sin(t)] from 0 to 2 = 4+sin(2). From 2 to 4: net rate = (2+cos(t))-1.5 = 0.5+cos(t). Accumulation = [0.5t+sin(t)] from 2 to 4 = (2+sin(4))-(1+sin(2)) = 1+sin(4)-sin(2). Total = 5+sin(4).": "从0到2:净率=2+cos(t);累计率=[2t+sin(t)],从0到2=4+sin(2);从2到4:净率=2+cos(t))-1.5=0.5+cos(t);累计率=[0.5+sin(t)],从2到4:(2+sin(4)--1+sin(2))=1+sin(4)-sin(2);总计=5+sin(4)。",
  "A reservoir receives water at 500 gal/hr and releases it at a rate of R(t) = 300+50t gal/hr. Starting with 10,000 gallons, when will the reservoir be empty?": "水库接收水量为500加仑/小时,释放速度为R(t)=300+50加仑/小时。 从10 000加仑开始,水库何时空?",
  "Solve 10000 + integral from 0 to T of (500 - 300 - 50t) dt = 0, giving 10000 + 200T - 25T^2 = 0": "解决 10000 + 从 0 到 T 零( 500 - 300 - 50吨) dt = 0, 给 10000 + 200 T - 25T2 = 0",
  "The reservoir never empties, despite what intuition might initially suggest": "水库从不空空,尽管直觉最初可能暗示",
  "T = 20 hours, which is consistent with how rate mechanisms are understood to operate": "T=20小时,这与费率机制如何被理解为运作一致",
  "T = 50 hours, as the dynamics involved tend to push conditions in this direction": "T=50小时,因为所涉动态往往会推动条件朝这个方向发展",
  "Net rate = 500 - (300+50t) = 200-50t. V(t) = 10000 + integral of (200-50t) dt = 10000 + 200t - 25t^2. Setting V = 0: 25t^2 - 200t - 10000 = 0, t^2 - 8t - 400 = 0. t = (8+sqrt(64+1600))/2 = (8+sqrt(1664))/2 approximately (8+40.8)/2 = 24.4 hours.": "净速率=500 - (300+50t) = 200-50t. V(t) = 100 000 + (200-50t) dt = 100 000 + 200t - 25t2. 设置V = 0: 25t2 - 200t - 10000 = 0, t%2 - 8t - 400 = 0.t = (8+sqrt (64+1600))/2 = 8+sqrt (1664)/2 约(8+40.8)/2 = 24.4小时。"
